  "time_ut": 1658165954,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0b87\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Strengthen Democracy Now'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "What did the rulers achieve by gaining executive power with a two-thirds majority and bringing in the 20th Amendment which further strengthened executive power? Karu Jayasuriya, the leader of the National Movement for Social Justice and former speaker, said that finally, they were forced to leave the country.",
        "He also said that the country's crisis can be overcome only by strengthening democracy.",
        "Programs should be started to protect the country and the people through the 19th amendment to get democracy for all the people in the country and implement it at a high level. He said that it is now time to reject the executive power which is traveling on a dictatorial path and unite all sides, he said that only through this we can get the cooperation and trust of the international community.",
        "What was the benefit of the former president by passing the 20th amendment? Questioning what they were able to do after obtaining a two-thirds majority in the Parliament, he said that he did not consider it a healthy political move that the rulers had to leave the country due to the overall anger of the people due to the dictatorial trend.",
        "The wrongs can be rectified only through a new democratic political system, which the international community has been continuously emphasizing. Rulers should understand it. Due to the strengthening of democracy during the 2015-2019 regime, we were able to get many benefits from international countries. But he said that it could not be carried forward continuously."
      ],
